<br />\n<br />\n...<br />\n<br />\n布林肯還批評，中國對香港的所作所為「非常過分」，破壞讓香港維持自治的承諾。北京通過影響深遠的港區國安法，明定分裂和顛覆罪名後，已對支持民主示威者發動一波波逮捕行動。<br />\n<br />\n布林肯受訪時說，美國必須對逃離鎮壓的的香港人打開大門，如同英國承諾所做的。<br />\n<br />\n他表示：「我們見到香港人再度起身捍衛自身權利，這些權利是原本保證會給他們的。如果他們是中國當局打壓的受害者，我們應該做些事來提供他們避風港。」<br />\n<br />\nSource:<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3429238\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3429238&d=FyOxfEvlGqeE3CGJWKQQl9C8ckn1nBU%2Fwr2%2FVciPwp8%3D&h=6b7f20a3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3429238&h=acd2be24\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3429238</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3429211\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3429211&d=FyOxfEvlGqeE3CGJWKQQl9C8ckn1nBU%2Fwr2%2FVciPwp8%3D&h=96d3570d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3429211&h=ab1aa2ce\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3429211</a>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T00:52:24.000Z","msg":"所有選項都只係戰略性忍耐,淨講唔做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}